              li.fragment Babylon.js
              li.fragment Phaser
              li.fragment PlayCanvas
              li.fragment A-Frame
          section.vertical-slide
            h1 A-Frame facts
            p Created by Mozilla at the end of 2015
            p.fragment Open-source, version 0.5.0 as of June 2017.
            p.fragment Focused on creating virtual reality experiences
            p.fragment  Perfect for all us front-enders to get started with 3D dev. 
